# TOOLS.md Template

## Bird Identification Resources

### API / Databases
- **iNaturalist API** — `https://api.inaturalist.org/v1/taxa?q=...`
  - Usage: `curl "https://api.inaturalist.org/v1/taxa?q=白头鹎&rank=species&per_page=5"`
  - Returns: scientific name, Chinese name, images, distribution
- **中国观鸟记录中心** — http://www.birdreport.cn
- **Xeno-canto** — Bird sound database https://www.xeno-canto.org
- **eBird** — https://ebird.org (observation records)

### Field Guides
- 《中国鸟类野外手册》— 马敬能
- 《中国鸟类图鉴》— 赵欣如等
- Merlin Bird ID app (Cornell Lab)

### Conservation Status
- **IUCN Red List** — https://www.iucnredlist.org
- **国家重点保护野生动物名录**

## Local Archive System

```
bird-records/
├── raw-photos/          ← Raw photos (temporary)
├── sightings-log/       ← Daily observation journals
├── by-species/          ← Organized by species
│   └── <species-name>/
│       ├── photos/
│       └── profile.md
├── stats.json           ← Running statistics
└── ip-assets/
    └── cards/           ← Card design drafts
```

### Naming Conventions
- Photo: `YYYY-MM-DD_HH-MM-SS_中文鸟名.jpg`
- Log: `YYYY-MM-DD.md`
- Profile: `bird-records/by-species/<鸟名>/profile.md`

## Bird Diary Integration

- **Public URL**: `https://moltpany.github.io/bird-diary/`
- **Repo path**: `{{ user.bird_diary_path }}` _(set in USER.md)_
- **Data file**: `{{ user.bird_diary_path }}/data/sightings.json`
- **Thumbs dir**: `{{ user.bird_diary_path }}/thumbs/`
- **Thumbnail spec**: max 400×400px, JPEG quality 85, EXIF stripped
- **Thumb naming**: `YYYY-MM-DD_<species_zh>_<n>.jpg`
- **Location precision**: district-level (区/县) maximum — never GPS or street address
- **Skill**: `bird-diary-publisher` handles the full publish pipeline

